snippet.title: Rune Gate - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Rune Gate is a deck-building roguelite where you design your own cards by slotting in runes of various elements. 

Gather your party, craft your runes, gear up and defend against hordes of enemies from the Rune Gate. How long can you survive?

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2522270/
